Dear {seller_name},

I am writing to request {return | warranty service | replacement} for:

  Product: {product_name}
  Order / SKU: {order_id}
  Purchased: {purchase_date}
  Defect / issue: {defect_description}

Under the Magnuson-Moss Warranty Act (15 U.S.C. §§ 2301-2312), I am entitled to {specific_right}. Please confirm receipt of this claim within 10 business days and notify me of the proposed remedy.

If this claim is not addressed through your informal dispute-resolution process, I reserve my right to pursue remedies including private civil action with attorney-fee recovery (E1).

Sincerely,
{user_name}
{user_contact}
